Subject: drm/msm/dpu: in dpu_format replace bitmap with unsigned long field
Git-commit: 932733b89f8b36dce623beccdb6ae4a9a128bf7a
Patch-mainline: v6.10-rc1
References: jsc#PED-9898 jsc#PED-10191 jsc#PED-10197 jsc#PED-10226 jsc#PED-10237 jsc#PED-10340 jsc#PED-10852 jsc#PED-11022

Using bitmap for the flags results in a clumsy syntax on test_bit,
replace it with unsigned long type and simple binary ops.

Reviewed-by: Abhinav Kumar <quic_abhinavk@quicinc.com>
Signed-off-by: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@linaro.org>
